{"tid":239944,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【瑞聲疑雲】沽空報告都造假！葛咸城P圖被踢爆","createTime":"2017-05-12T04:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T01:49:12.000Z","uid":9031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ced423b436cf430daf86d3712e66c86343ad597","tid":239944,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T04:44:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/PS6XFui.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPS6XFui.png&h=a2af3d7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「葛咸城研究」昨日發沽空報告質疑瑞聲科技（2018）造假，點知被內地傳媒發現報告有造假成分，驚見P圖！<br />\n<br />\n話說「葛咸城研究」表示，瑞聲有超過20間未披露的關連方，違反客戶蘋果的規則，其中一家叫「連泰精密科技江蘇有限公司」，在沽空報告顯示的外貎照片，外牆印上「瑞聲科技」紅字，而非公司本身名字，並聲稱連泰精密是由瑞聲的CEO擁有。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0YecvfK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0YecvfK.png&h=126e0972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過，「葛咸城研究」P圖技巧似乎有待改進，紅字（圖1）似乎與外圍電纜線重疊，肉眼已經睇到係P圖。記者於騰訊地圖，按「葛咸城研究」提供的地址「江蘇省沭陽縣沭城鎮永嘉路40號」搜尋，亦能搜尋到外貎完全相同的廠房（圖2），並是同一角度的照片，但外牆紅字是寫上「鴻利達鋁業」而非「瑞聲科技」。留意返，騰訊地圖顯示的圖片為2014年5月拍攝。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170512/56683251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170512%2F56683251&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUip7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=be4c8df5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170512%2F56683251&h=bd50893a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170512/56683251</a>"},{"pid":"f7c90a50576b9668ceaf809fc832cec7de1b3217","tid":239944,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T04:46:30.000Z","msg":"留名等花生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590c1b3b8c0e7de1cefb713306071738302a8721","tid":239944,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T04:48:04.000Z","msg":"如果真係造假隨時告撚到甩褲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.g